					"stroke": "#FF4D00",
					"textAlign": "left",
					"fontFamily": "Lucida Grande",
					"fontSize": 13,
					"text": "Do not attempt to open this HDI in Design mode using this version; if you do so, forms and/or methods could be altered because of missing functionality."
